ast Resistance</span><hr size=1> Proof, once again, that if you take away constraints, people will naturally, like water, take the path of least resistance. <br><br><br>As far as I'm concerned, if they want to call this the &quot;roleplay preferred&quot; server, they need to re-institute the alignment restrictions. <br><br>But I don't think it really matters. Everquest is a social game that isn't designed well for roleplaying. I suspect there are a few next-generation RPG's on the horizon that will fill this void. <br><br>-Krazak  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utzarothfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tzaroth FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 153<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/16/02 4:43:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1228.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Firiona Vie (Convenience Preferred)</span><hr size=1> Did anyone else read Bobmato's response?<br><br>That's a terrific idea. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ulothraem.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lothraem</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.delharen.com/images/sword.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/16/02 4:53:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1228.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Firiona Vie (Convenience Preferred)</span><hr size=1> I actually see both sides.<br><br>As an evil Shadow Knight (which I play with honor and chivalre despite his totally wicked designs, one can b